ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I could hardly think of advanced game theory being taught in a more efficient way.
It is a overall look over the game theory. it is a great class.

I would recommend this class to any student interested in using game theory in their research. For a political science student, this course is a helpful (but challenging) extension to the polisci game theory classes.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: An economist with little or no knowledge of advanced game theory is like a poet who is unlettered. In this sense, this course is everything.
I need to know the material presented in this course to understand papers in my own field better, and I guess this course did a pretty good job helping me understand those papers better.
